Pre-Game Insights: The Braves have been in a pseudo-do-or-die mode for a while now, but on Wednesday night, they will face their second elimination game in three contests.
Max Fried is starting for the Braves on regular rest. He finished the regular season with 3.4 fWAR in 29 starts (174 1/3 innings).
Joe Musgrove is starting for the Padres. He posted 1.4 fWAR in 19 starts spanning 99 2/3 innings despite missing a huge part of the season with elbow inflammation.
